Vandle Analysis Software Toolkit (VAST)
---------------------------------------------

Some prerequisites:
pugixml >= 1.2
ROOT+RooFit >= 5.99/03


1. SETTING UP 
  A) Config.xml
     The idea here is that all of the major bits of the config file are 
     handled by their respective classes. The exceptions are the Author,
     Description, and Flags parts. I expect things are going to be tweaky
     for a bit until things get going. 